ng\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/2017/06/13/bonjour-de-paris/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 13 Jun 2017 14:21:04 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:318:\"\n		        A few months ago, we asked you to send us postcards. For us it was a great way to get news from meetups and WordCamps from all over Europe. We always praise the ever-growing number of WordPress gatherings and we wanted to see the faces of these communities. It was great to get news from [&#8230;]		        \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"WordCamp Europe\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5337:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7699 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/Pasted-image-at-2017_06_13-01_40-PM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"800\" /></p>\n<p>A few months ago, we asked you to send us postcards. For us it was a great way to get news from meetups and WordCamps from all over Europe. We always praise the ever-growing number of WordPress gatherings and we wanted to see the faces of these communities. It was great to get news from all of you while working on the massive event that is WordCamp Europe. We clearly hope that the WordCamp Europe will keep the spirit of these peopleーboth amateurs and professionalsーspending few hours together at night to share, learn and have fun around WordPress.<span id=\"more-7682\"></span></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7683\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7683 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/wordcamp-sevilla.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"575\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">And we did have fun at Sevilla two years ago. Muchas gracias!</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7685\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7685 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/meetup-marbella.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"575\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">And another one from Andalucia, a place of palm trees, sun and WordPress.</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7686\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7686 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/meetup-cologne.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"575\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hallo Köln! Danke sehr <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" /></figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7696\" style=\"width: 640px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7696 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/meetup-hamburg.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"472\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ziemlich Möwen Hamburg!</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7687\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7687 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/meetup-lodz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"575\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cześć Łódź! Dziękuję <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" /></figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7695\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7695 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/wordcamp-kiev.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"575\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">привіт Київ (I hope I didn&#8217;t mess with this one)</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7694\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7694 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/meetup-zagreb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"575\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dobro jutro Zagreb!</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7684\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7684 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/meetup-paris.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"575\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">We are ready to welcome you. A bientôt!</figcaption></figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Some sent us real cards (yes they still exist!).</span></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7688\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7688 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/wordcamp-bordeaux.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"630\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">This year France held a new WordCamp in the beautiful city of Bordeaux. Salut les amis!</figcaption></figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">And finally, Isabelle sent us a postcard from Thailand while she was travelling, because WordPress is about discovering as much as you can <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" /></span></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7689 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/bangkok-postcard.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"1137\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">We hope that your next destination will be Paris in a few days. We wish you all the best for the future. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"🙂\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em;max-height: 1em\" /> </span></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7690\" style=\"width: 780px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-7690 size-full\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/carte-souvenir-bonjour-paris.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"513\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">To finish, something vintage. This postcard depicts la Ville des Lumières over a century ago.</figcaption></figure><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpfr/~4/0eyLKYll1ys\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/2017/06/13/bonjour-de-paris/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"\n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:4:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thank you #WCEU media partners!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpfr/~3/ro1mgY28qZE/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/2017/06/12/thank-you-wceu-media-partners/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 12 Jun 2017 12:15:39 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:369:\"\n		        2017 was the first year we introduced the possibility for media outlets to become media partners of WordCamp Europe. Without further ado, we would like to welcome and say a big thank you to our media partners KrautPress.de, Torquemag.io, and WP Tavern. KrautPress.de KrautPress has deep roots in the German WP community. Its a publication [&#8230;]		        \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"WordCamp Europe\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2450:\"<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-7502 aligncenter\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/06/media-partners-thanks.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"800\" />2017 was the first year we introduced the possibility for media outlets to become media partners of WordCamp Europe. Without further ado, we would like to welcome and say a big thank you to our media partners <a href=\"https://krautpress.de/\">KrautPress.de</a>, <a href=\"https://torquemag.io/\">Torquemag.io</a>, and <a href=\"https://wptavern.com/\">WP Tavern</a>.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-7498\"></span></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>KrautPress.de</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://krautpress.de/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-6169 alignright\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/05/krautpress.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"200\" /></a>KrautPress has deep roots in the German WP community. Its a publication with great content for both beginners and WP professionals. In 2016 KrautPress entered the German WP Planet feed and gained a lot of audience. This year the team is getting bigger and plan to publish six e-papers focused on one specific topic per issue. KrautPress audience is as diverse as the community itself &#8211; hobby bloggers, designers, developers, activists and podcasters (and they also have their own podcast too :))</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Torquemag.io</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://torquemag.io/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-6170 alignright\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/05/torque.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"200\" /></a>Torque Magazine is a leading resource for WordPress news. Content equips new and advanced WordPress users with expert insights and information to help them create, grow, and optimise their WordPress sites and build better experiences online. Torque Magazine has a global audience and features stories and insights from contributors from all over the world.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>WPTavern.com</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://wptavern.com/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-6171 alignright\" src=\"http://2017.europe.wordcamp.org/files/2017/05/wotavern.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"200\" /></a>WP Tavern is one of the most active sources of WordPress news, essentially WordPress&#8217; paper of record. WordPress Tavern is a warm and inviting community where those interested in the software can hang out with fellow WordPressers to engage in enlightening discussions.</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpfr/~4/ro1mgY28qZE\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://2017.e